{"tid":1110781,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"其實睇中醫有冇料到","createTime":"2019-04-16T16:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T11:27:54.000Z","uid":151858,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9c65141fbb84146519edcdd97c3e5058f54c0549","tid":1110781,"uid":151858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T16:29:05.000Z","msg":"自己個人經常捱夜又飲得少水<br />\n仲要呢排考試就更加少訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排覺得自己條利底好似腫腫地<br />\n又成日覺得個人冇乜力好易覺得攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢一年仲好似生多左暗瘡咁<br />\n唔知關唔關自己飲多左好多酒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大個人都未睇過中醫<br />\n其實係咪真係可以調理下等個人冇咁虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5dfd0d453a8d2a759c2c1f39d568854627981e","tid":1110781,"uid":46752,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"ec1554a6da2ca7cac4aed9dee0f5f720f0fae641","tid":1110781,"uid":35069,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"慢性調理係有用嘅，但都要你自己肯配合調整返作息飲食之類，如果唔係咩中藥西藥都無用"},{"pid":"7c5eba6b432f8a4944dfec6cde161945b334645d","tid":1110781,"uid":151858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec1554a6da2ca7cac4aed9dee0f5f720f0fae641","tid":1110781,"uid":35069,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"慢性調理係有用嘅，但都要你自己肯配合調整返作息飲食之類，如果唔係咩中藥西藥都無用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"我都覺得要飲多啲水同早啲訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e291653a1e7faaace3d41e4e5aeaab3425ee0c","tid":1110781,"uid":151858,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T17:35:38.000Z","msg":"係咪睇番中醫診所好啲 藥房果啲中醫是咪冇咁掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6f402a72f5f979a94453ad631e0b4ccc7b101b","tid":1110781,"uid":46752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score